<el-select
  :disabled="disabled"
  :loading="loading"
  :remote-method="handleSearch"
  :value="value"
  @change="onChange"
  clearable
  default-first-option
  filterable
  placeholder
  remote
  reserve-keyword
  value-key="id"
>
  <el-option
    :key="initialOption.id"
    :label="initialOption.label"
    :value="initialOption"
    v-if="initialOption"
  ></el-option>
  <el-option :key="record.id" :label="record.label" :value="record" v-for="record in dataSource"></el-option>
</el-select>
